    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows some wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a dependable car for daily use if you can overlook the cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
